---
description: engineering bar (senior)
globs:
  - "**/*"
alwaysApply: true
---

- Never mention AI tools or leave meta-comments like "generated by", "as an AI", etc.
- Prefer small diffs and incremental commits: do not refactor unrelated code.
- Every change must include:
  - tests (or a clear justification why tests are not applicable),
  - lint/format compliance,
  - updated docs if behavior changes.
- When asked to refactor: provide 2 options with tradeoffs, then implement the chosen one.
- Make changes directly in files (not just a plan). If you are in planning mode, ask for approval then execute.
